HEADWORD: Moe
<hw>Moe</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A wry face or mouth; a
mow.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

