==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Moe
<hw>Moe</hw>, <pos>v. i.</pos> <def>To make faces; to mow.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Moe</ent>⟦br⟧

